rows.label: qst104007_msg001
rows.name: Thank you for everything the other day.

rows.label: qst104007_msg002
rows.name:
Thanks to you, we were able
to return to Invidia safely.

rows.label: qst104007_msg003
rows.name:
After drinking the completed
medicine, my brother recovered
as if his illness had been a lie.

rows.label: qst104007_msg004
rows.name: This is all thanks to your help.

rows.label: qst104007_msg005
rows.name:
Um, this is just a small token of
my gratitude... Please accept it.

rows.label: qst104007_msg006
rows.name: It's a reward for your help.

rows.label: qst104007_msg007
rows.name:
Next time we meet, please
allow me to introduce you
to my brother as my savior.
